The paper deals with path planning for robotic sensor platforms, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of Gaussian process regression for estimating measurement values falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves environmental mapping, which can be categorized under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of multiple UAVs and the need to operate under constraints falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper involves decision-making and optimization, which can be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG).
